00:33:12,190 --> 00:33:14,050
Take a look at today's newspaper.

611
00:33:16,790 --> 00:33:18,520
I'd like this daily newspaper.

612
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:33,890
Mom.

613
00:33:35,790 --> 00:33:36,580
Changcheng.

614
00:33:37,850 --> 00:33:38,650
Where's Mom?

615
00:33:39,460 --> 00:33:40,580
Isn't Mom in her room?

616
00:33:40,580 --> 00:33:41,980
She's not in her room.

617
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:43,420
Not there?

618
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,560
Go look for her quickly.

619
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:46,070
Make sure she hasn't wandered off.

620
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:46,800
I'll go look.

621
00:33:50,490 --> 00:33:50,840
Mom.

622
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:52,760
Mom.

623
00:33:52,780 --> 00:33:54,190
I went to buy a newspaper.

624
00:33:54,530 --> 00:33:55,860
And got some breakfast.

625
00:33:58,070 --> 00:34:00,130
Steamed buns and fried dough sticks.

626
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:01,660
That's so much trouble for you,

627
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:03,660
going out so early to buy breakfast.

628
00:34:03,980 --> 00:34:05,320
You're always spending money on us.

629
00:34:05,320 --> 00:34:06,280
Not at all.

630
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:10,050
Fried dough sticks barely cost anything.

631
00:34:10,989 --> 00:34:12,280
Go ahead and eat.

632
00:34:13,230 --> 00:34:15,159
It's fine. We'll wait for you, Mom.

633
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:15,840
Coming.

634
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:23,389
Changcheng.

635
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:25,280
This tie looks nice.

636
00:34:25,300 --> 00:34:26,060
Yes, it suits me perfectly.

637
00:34:26,060 --> 00:34:27,020
It looks good on you.

638
00:34:27,020 --> 00:34:27,350
Yes.

639
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:29,469
Thank you for the gift, Mom.

640
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:32,620
By the way, Mom.

641
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:35,020
Were you listening
to the radio last night?

642
00:34:36,770 --> 00:34:39,130
I was probably too excited yesterday.

643
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,850
So I couldn't sleep well at night.

644
00:34:40,850 --> 00:34:41,860
I just wanted to listen

645
00:34:41,860 --> 00:34:43,170
to something nice.

646
00:34:43,199 --> 00:34:44,670
I didn't disturb you, did I?

647
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:45,460
No, not at all.

648
00:34:45,460 --> 00:34:46,190
That's good.

649
00:34:46,510 --> 00:34:47,239
Changcheng.

650
00:34:49,489 --> 00:34:50,239
Ju.

651
00:34:50,260 --> 00:34:52,159
I don't love
salted duck eggs as much as you do.

652
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:54,230
I remember you used to
eat salted duck eggs with porridge

653
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:55,850
and could finish two bowls, right?

654
00:34:55,850 --> 00:34:56,510
Really?

655
00:34:56,540 --> 00:34:57,550
Ju, eat up.

656
00:34:58,340 --> 00:35:01,200
Mom, my taste
has become milder since I had the baby.

657
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,030
You have it.

658
00:35:04,890 --> 00:35:05,470
Here.

659
00:35:05,790 --> 00:35:06,940
Ju, have this.

660
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:07,890
Mom's is here.

661
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,880
Ju, Changcheng.

662
00:35:15,250 --> 00:35:17,310
I want to discuss something with you.

663
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:20,340
I think starting from today,

664
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,920
let me

665
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:23,830
take care of the food expenses.

666
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:24,730
Is that okay?

667
00:35:25,170 --> 00:35:25,880
After all,

668
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:27,980
I came here to support you.

669
00:35:28,010 --> 00:35:28,690
Right?

670
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,170
You need to raise a baby.

671
00:35:30,170 --> 00:35:31,700
And your expenses are high.

672
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:32,760
Please don't.

673
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:35,230
We don't have much to offer you.

674
00:35:35,580 --> 00:35:37,070
We already feel embarrassed.

675
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:38,560
How could we spend your money?

676
00:35:38,560 --> 00:35:40,660
Yes, you came from so far away to help us.

677
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:42,230
And you're always
worrying about our livelihood.

678
00:35:42,230 --> 00:35:44,030
This really isn't appropriate.

679
00:35:44,520 --> 00:35:46,450
At my trading company in Hong Kong,

680
00:35:46,620 --> 00:35:48,390
I'm the financial director.

681
00:35:48,530 --> 00:35:50,460
My income is quite substantial.

682
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:52,300
Besides, if I don't

683
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:54,180
spend this money on you, who else?

684
00:35:54,270 --> 00:35:56,420
Should I just let it
gather dust in the suitcase?

685
00:35:56,420 --> 00:35:58,430
I can't just stay
and eat at your place for free.

686
00:35:58,430 --> 00:35:59,230
Right?

687
00:35:59,570 --> 00:36:00,110
Mom.

688
00:36:00,940 --> 00:36:03,800
That will make
Changcheng and me feel embarrassed.

689
00:36:04,310 --> 00:36:05,060
Ju.

690
00:36:05,650 --> 00:36:08,150
You're family but talking like strangers.

691
00:36:08,630 --> 00:36:10,230
If you keep being so formal,

692
00:36:10,730 --> 00:36:12,510
I'm going to be upset.

693
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:17,730
Okay, I won't be so formal with you, Mom.

694
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:18,740
Thank you, Mom.

695
00:36:18,980 --> 00:36:20,320
Good. That's better.

696
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:22,050
Let's eat now.

697
00:36:28,650 --> 00:36:29,660
Mom hasn't started eating yet.

698
00:36:29,660 --> 00:36:30,730
I was going to give this to Mom.

699
00:36:30,730 --> 00:36:31,300
Here, Mom.

700
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:33,700
I already have some.
Well, okay. Thank you.

701
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:48,910
Mom, now that you're here,

702
00:36:48,930 --> 00:36:50,860
you should stay for a while, right?

703
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:54,360
I'm worried Mom might leave soon.

704
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:56,220
That's why I'm trying
to put Mom's mind at ease.

705
00:36:56,220 --> 00:36:56,930
You...

706
00:36:57,410 --> 00:36:59,700
I'll stay as long as you want me to.

707
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,750
I came here to help you anyway.

708
00:37:02,230 --> 00:37:04,670
Mom, of course I hope you can stay longer.

709
00:37:06,570 --> 00:37:08,050
Yes, I hope so too.

710
00:37:08,520 --> 00:37:09,690
We were just talking about it.

711
00:37:09,690 --> 00:37:10,850
Since Mom arrived,

712
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,810
Ju's condition has improved a lot.

713
00:37:14,620 --> 00:37:15,920
If you welcome me,

714
00:37:16,460 --> 00:37:17,720
I'll stay a bit longer.

