00:38:07,470 --> 00:38:08,070
Director.

717
00:38:08,200 --> 00:38:08,910
Busy?

718
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:13,600
Director.

719
00:38:14,020 --> 00:38:14,550
Morning.

720
00:38:47,770 --> 00:38:48,310
Leader.

721
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:50,510
Come in.

722
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:56,750
The car is ready.

723
00:38:58,880 --> 00:38:59,440
Good.

724
00:38:59,730 --> 00:39:00,360
By the way,

725
00:39:00,870 --> 00:39:03,400
have someone
take this suitcase downstairs.

726
00:39:06,300 --> 00:39:09,430
Leader, are you really
going to the Taichung mountains?

727
00:39:11,030 --> 00:39:11,830
What's wrong?

728
00:39:13,160 --> 00:39:16,420
Chongqing and Guiyang
may be closer to the Communist Army,

729
00:39:16,640 --> 00:39:18,240
but at least they're cities.

730
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:21,190
Up in the Taichung mountains,
it's such a godforsaken place

731
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:22,890
that only the birds
bother to take a dump there.

732
00:39:22,890 --> 00:39:24,550
What's worth going there for?

733
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:29,840
Isn't Liu Kangfu
from the Taiwan Work Committee?

734
00:39:30,420 --> 00:39:32,660
I believe Deputy Chief Wu's upcoming work

735
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:34,340
will definitely involve
the Taiwan Work Committee.

736
00:39:34,340 --> 00:39:36,030
Getting to know
their grassroots operations

737
00:39:36,030 --> 00:39:36,850
can't hurt, right?

738
00:39:36,850 --> 00:39:37,810
At a time like this,

739
00:39:37,810 --> 00:39:39,940
you're still thinking about the case?

740
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:43,020
You don't understand.

741
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:52,060
Leader.

742
00:40:04,080 --> 00:40:04,650
Please.

743
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:08,730
Mr. Gu,

744
00:40:09,580 --> 00:40:10,980
why haven't you left yet?

745
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,400
What a situation this is.

746
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,830
The Director asked me to temporarily

747
00:40:16,830 --> 00:40:18,290
take over the Counterintelligence Section.

748
00:40:18,290 --> 00:40:20,090
I deliberately timed my arrival

749
00:40:20,550 --> 00:40:22,030
to avoid making you uncomfortable,

750
00:40:22,030 --> 00:40:23,130
but I still came too early...

751
00:40:23,130 --> 00:40:23,840
Mr. Ye.

752
00:40:26,190 --> 00:40:29,390
That's not how
we drive in Counterintelligence Section.

753
00:40:29,460 --> 00:40:30,790
How should I drive then?

754
00:40:32,730 --> 00:40:33,660
Watch your tone.

755
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,060
Are you alright?

756
00:40:38,060 --> 00:40:38,650
I'm fine.

757
00:40:40,130 --> 00:40:41,390
It's good I came early.

758
00:40:41,520 --> 00:40:42,450
I'll see you off.

759
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:43,420
No need.

760
00:40:43,450 --> 00:40:45,130
That's thoughtful of you. Thanks.

761
00:40:45,130 --> 00:40:45,900
Uh...

762
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:48,800
Mr. Ye, I'd like to ask you a favor.

763
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:49,530
You see,

764
00:40:49,900 --> 00:40:50,840
these men

765
00:40:51,560 --> 00:40:53,130
all came from the Operations Division,

766
00:40:53,130 --> 00:40:54,220
and you know them all.

767
00:40:54,220 --> 00:40:56,080
They'll be working under you now,

768
00:40:56,130 --> 00:40:56,730
so please

769
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:57,800
take good care of them.

770
00:40:57,800 --> 00:40:59,180
No need to be so formal.

771
00:41:00,170 --> 00:41:01,190
We're brothers.

772
00:41:01,210 --> 00:41:01,790
Yes, yes.

773
00:41:01,820 --> 00:41:03,880
We all used to be in the same division.

774
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,170
I am a man of principles.

775
00:41:06,850 --> 00:41:08,870
I'll never play favorites.

776
00:41:09,030 --> 00:41:09,650
Yes, yes.

777
00:41:09,910 --> 00:41:12,310
Pickled beans with rice will be plentiful,

778
00:41:12,370 --> 00:41:13,480
but as for bonuses,

779
00:41:14,110 --> 00:41:15,860
that depends on their own luck.

780
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:16,950
Yes, yes.

781
00:41:17,180 --> 00:41:18,380
Did you all hear that?

782
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:20,190
Work hard under Mr. Ye,

783
00:41:20,310 --> 00:41:22,510
and you'll definitely be treated well.

784
00:41:30,510 --> 00:41:31,070
Alright.

785
00:41:32,040 --> 00:41:33,300
Get in the car quickly.

786
00:41:33,950 --> 00:41:34,900
Get in the car.

787
00:41:50,690 --> 00:41:51,360
Director.

788
00:41:52,150 --> 00:41:53,860
We can't find the file
of Zhang Hao's case.

789
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:56,010
It's not in the archives room
or the file cabinets.

790
00:41:56,010 --> 00:41:56,970
That's right.

791
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:59,650
It's best if he takes

792
00:42:01,470 --> 00:42:02,870
this hot potato with him.

793
00:42:34,780 --> 00:42:36,690
Nie Xi, I've moved out.

794
00:42:37,750 --> 00:42:39,730
Your lies about our child

795
00:42:40,040 --> 00:42:41,770
are something I can't forgive.

796
00:42:42,030 --> 00:42:44,430
Perhaps I can sleep better somewhere else.

797
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:45,970
I've left you

798
00:42:46,460 --> 00:42:47,920
a photo of our child.

799
00:42:49,330 --> 00:42:50,860
I hope when you see her face,

800
00:42:51,310 --> 00:42:52,970
you'll miss her as much as I do.

801
00:42:54,270 --> 00:42:55,020
Mei.

